Package ohos.telephony

Class CellularDataStateObserver

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.telephony.CellularDataStateObserver

  • public class CellularDataStateObserver
extends Object
    Observes state updates of cellular data services.

    This class can observe updates of the uplink and downlink data flow states and the data link connection state.

    Since:
    1
